2025-09-03T07:15:40:           '#1976D2' as color,
2025-09-03T07:15:40:           COALESCE(SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))), 0) as total_hours,
2025-09-03T07:15:40:           COUNT(te.id) as entry_count
2025-09-03T07:15:40:         FROM projects p
2025-09-03T07:15:40:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-03T07:15:40:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-03T07:15:40:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-03T07:15:40:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-03T07:15:40:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-03T07:15:40:         
2025-09-03T07:15:40:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-03T07:15:40:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC
2025-09-03T07:15:40:

2025-09-03T08:09:57:           COALESCE(SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))), 0) as total_hours,
2025-09-03T08:09:57:           COUNT(te.id) as entry_count
2025-09-03T08:09:57:         FROM projects p
2025-09-03T08:09:57:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-03T08:09:57:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-03T08:09:57:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-03T08:09:57:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-03T08:09:57:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-03T08:09:57:         
2025-09-03T08:09:57:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-03T08:09:57:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC
2025-09-03T08:09:57:

2025-09-03T08:36:55:           p.name,
2025-09-03T08:36:55:           '#1976D2' as color,
2025-09-03T08:36:55:           COALESCE(SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))), 0) as total_hours,
2025-09-03T08:36:55:           COUNT(te.id) as entry_count
2025-09-03T08:36:55:         FROM projects p
2025-09-03T08:36:55:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-03T08:36:55:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-03T08:36:55:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-03T08:36:55:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-03T08:36:55:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-03T08:36:55:         
2025-09-03T08:36:55:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-03T08:36:55:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC
2025-09-03T08:36:55:

2025-09-03T09:48:00:           '#1976D2' as color,
2025-09-03T09:48:00:           COALESCE(SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))), 0) as total_hours,

2025-09-03T09:48:00:         FROM projects p
2025-09-03T09:48:00:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-03T09:48:00:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-03T09:48:00:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-03T09:48:00:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-03T09:48:00:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-03T09:48:00:         
2025-09-03T09:48:00:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-03T09:48:00:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC
